data.name: label1.Text
data.value:
An order upon delivery of goods by third-party courier services - upon receipt, be sure to check the availability of all goods in the order, as well as its appearance. In case of damage to the goods, or incomplete order picking, it is necessary to refuse to receive the goods and pay for them, as well as draw up an act (claim).
Be sure to inform us of what happened by calling: (044) 000 - 00 - 00

data.name: label9.Text
data.value:
Payment by bank transfer is made at the cash desk of a branch of any bank or from the settlement account of your company
When choosing a non-cash payment method, delivery of the order is possible after receipt of funds in our current account
